{"tid":2122686,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉載］給予bno想留阿爸搵錢既朋友","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T07:39:06.000Z","uid":117420,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7bb0854ab573fca890cbc8e250f53aa96246191","tid":2122686,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108411397560878/posts/151242569944427/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108411397560878%2Fposts%2F151242569944427%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=b4cdd818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108411397560878/posts/151242569944427/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n太空人會影響小朋友申請求居！<br />\n太空人會影響小朋友申請求居！<br />\n太空人會影響小朋友申請求居！<br />\n<br />\n就太空人的問題，網上眾說紛紜。翻看條例後，此舉會影響18歲以下子女將來申請永居。<br />\n<br />\n特意查看了現時兒童申請永居的要求，根據(Immigration rules part 8, clause 298)：<br />\n<br />\n兒童（18歲以下）申請永居條件： <br />\n<br />\n(a) both parents are present and settled in the United Kingdom; or (父母雙方皆已有永居,最正常情況）<br />\n<br />\n跳至C項 （類似太空人情況）<br />\n(c) one parent is present and settled in the United Kingdom and has had sole responsibility for the child&rsquo;s upbringing or the child normally lives with this parent and not their other parent; or<br />\n<br />\n好啦，很多人話，我一個人在英國做太空人照顧小朋友,同佢一齊住，咪符合C囉。<br />\n<br />\n錯，內政部對咩係sole responsibility and child normally lives with this parent 係有定義的。<br />\n<br />\n即是要： <br />\n- sole responsibility 指父母其中一方負責兒童的重要決定，通常指放棄撫養權<br />\n- child normally lives with this parent and not their other parent 通常指已離異的父母，但有共同撫養權<br />\n<br />\n咁如果真係咁，5年後小朋友不能永居點算？唔通要離開英國？我都唔太清楚，估計是申請成為已拿永居的父/母的dependent?<br />\n<br />\n咁如果父母都有BNO，子女為dependent，必須一同申請嗎？<br />\n唔知，有人說跟family visa類比就要，如果與PBS dependent （如工作簽證dependent)即可分開申請。<br />\n<br />\n以上只供參考，請留意一月細節公佈。如果情況比較複雜者，建議向有牌adviser 查詢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/find-an-immigration-adviser\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ffind-an-immigration-adviser&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=c61408ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/find-an-immigration-adviser</a><br />\n<br />\n詳細定義請見 (p. 36 - 38): <a href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/902835/family-life-_as-a-partner-or-parent_-private-life-and-exceptional-circs-v9.0ext.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F902835%2Ffamily-life-_as-a-partner-or-parent_-private-life-and-exceptional-circs-v9.0ext.pdf&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=d1fc0192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/902835/family-life-_as-a-partner-or-parent_-private-life-and-exceptional-circs-v9.0ext.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/exodustalent/photos/a.125327629202588/151242536611097/?type=3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexodustalent%2Fphotos%2Fa.125327629202588%2F151242536611097%2F%3Ftype%3D3&h=3d8fb47c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9652c01d7e6a38b45ad1fd4661243206695cc6f0","tid":2122686,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"975c5cde4c2ea944e108dcd3ad24959d93320bbc","tid":2122686,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:42:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"488f49ba50674ec16330efa9e39c2274043b0769","tid":2122686,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab58a3d05653f37136a4ab4610b68762d06a21ef","tid":2122686,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:44:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8520ace536302ce00bb481b35a7fdaf6abb7f2ea","ti